      <para id="id5899329">2. No</para>
      <list id="id5454988" list-type="bulleted">
        <item>It will rise, because the little fish takes up the space of the water and the water has to take up some other space.</item>
        <item><emphasis effect="bold">Experiment:</emphasis> Accept any meaningful planning, for instance bicycle pump that cannot be pushed in completely if the opening is closed.</item>
